  "1902940": {
    "name": "Snacktorio",
    "steam_appid": 1902940,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很久以前，饥饿的巨兽企图吞噬世界，唯一的解决办法是用美食把它们的肚子填满！可是，怪兽越来越多，订单多到我们应付不过来了……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你受主厨邀请，加入了厨师旅团，负责建设运营新的烹饪工厂，持续为怪兽提供食物。获取食材、搭建生产线、烹制灵感源自世界各地的精致餐品，每一道都要满足某些非常挑剔的味蕾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >往返各个岛屿，寻找巨兽胃口大增的真相。你将发现全新的食材、规则以及意想不到的麻烦，你的工厂系统将面临巨大考验。你能平息巨兽的饥饿狂潮，同时证明自己“巫师林”星级厨师的身份吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/480a869b08c62b14bc9bb9f086d22c78.poster.avif?t=1771589584\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/480a869b08c62b14bc9bb9f086d22c78.webm?t=1771589584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/480a869b08c62b14bc9bb9f086d22c78.mp4?t=1771589584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>喂饱巨兽，维持和平</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接受饥饿巨兽的订单，制作多种美味餐食，每一道菜都要考虑口味、喜好和忌口。满足它们的需求，才能防止这座岛屿……不会变成它们的午餐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/2e59ee22f8a44b8b4196098c7989ccf0.poster.avif?t=1771589584\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/2e59ee22f8a44b8b4196098c7989ccf0.webm?t=1771589584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/2e59ee22f8a44b8b4196098c7989ccf0.mp4?t=1771589584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建设食品工厂</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用搅拌机、烤箱、锅炉、炸锅、分拣器和管道等设备，设计全自动厨房。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种食材都有自己的逻辑。随着生产规模扩大，你需要管理时间、污染、过敏原、保质期等各种细节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/11297fcac4acc5c705899e7f6880de4b.poster.avif?t=1771589584\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/11297fcac4acc5c705899e7f6880de4b.webm?t=1771589584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/11297fcac4acc5c705899e7f6880de4b.mp4?t=1771589584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>根据真实的规则驾驭食材</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乳制品遇热凝结，坚果传播过敏原，肉类可能导致食物中毒，而面团则会逐渐发酵。学习这些规则，然后加以利用，建设……大概不会崩溃的工厂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/797c497e9d597cc0faa199719bc5cbbe.poster.avif?t=1771589584\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/797c497e9d597cc0faa199719bc5cbbe.webm?t=1771589584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/797c497e9d597cc0faa199719bc5cbbe.mp4?t=1771589584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>探索逻辑各异的岛屿</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每座岛屿都有全新的核心食材、机制、危险和布局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁新的餐品，解决当地奇怪的问题，建造所需的工厂，免得巨兽惹祸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/52205715de6c223c8097df16ab120ae6.poster.avif?t=1771589584\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/52205715de6c223c8097df16ab120ae6.webm?t=1771589584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/52205715de6c223c8097df16ab120ae6.mp4?t=1771589584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>大规模解决多步骤的烹饪谜题</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把简单的食谱变成管道和机器构成的庞大网络。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制过于强力的食材，避免交叉污染，防止灾难性的凝结事故，顶住压力，维持生产运转。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/35181bed8f93240764946a29d8667f73.poster.avif?t=1771589584\" width=1170 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/35181bed8f93240764946a29d8667f73.webm?t=1771589584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1902940/extras/35181bed8f93240764946a29d8667f73.mp4?t=1771589584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>后期系统，离谱又美味</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着探索深入，你将需要用到虚能机器、灌注液体、蒸汽烹饪系统，还要为辛辣餐食提供消化促进方案，甚至还有多层甜点传送带，就这样进入越来越古怪的地方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的一部分收益将捐给饥饿救济、食品银行和食物浪费防治慈善机构，让现实世界需要帮助的人获得食物。</p>",
